ory-text\">Finally, citation-context services provide a complementary lens on how a paper is used in arguments and evidence chains. scite coverage is not available in the current pipeline output. <a href=\"https://scite.ai/reports/10.1111/add.70017\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">View scite report</a>.</p>",
